title: Too much Zed lately
body: Anyone getting annoyed at the amount of Zed players recently?

replies.body: I stopped maining zed because of this :'(
Play Zed, get inside the enemy {{champion:39}}
Zed has been rampant for months! Getting so sick of versing Zeds mid.
Changes are inbound, but yes there is quite an amount of Zed players as of late.

Ban him, if you're playing Ranked.

If in Norms tho, well gl, get Zhonya, Kayle or Liss.
